701239f-a.title: Bronx: Henry Hudson Parkway - 227th Street (West)
701239f-a.text:
(1)
Henry Hudson Parkway (Spuyten Duyvil Parkway), west side, north
from West 227th (left) to 230th Streets, showing a comprehensive
view of part of the Spuyten Duyvil section of the borough. IIn the
left background appears the Henry Hudson Monument.
About 1936.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
An exclusive view of the Henry Hudson Monument as seen from
Independence Ave.
May 25, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
